{"tid":2444960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美指華為、中興等五間中國企業威脅國家安全","createTime":"2021-03-13T08:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T11:55:10.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e67937dce6b7081795c76fc9b379ad521bf71260","tid":2444960,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"美指華為、中興等五間中國企業威脅國家安全<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427212&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=429f7fb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427212&h=0ee07836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427212</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國指，中國五間企業對國家安全構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n它們分別是華為、中興通訊、海能達通信、杭州海康威視數字技術公司，以及大華技術公司。<br />\n<br />\n國聯邦通訊委員會是按2019年《安全可靠通訊網絡法》要求，列出對美國國家安全構成不可接受威脅的企業清單。委員會指，今次的清單能夠提供具意義的指引，確保美國建立新一代通訊網絡時，不會用到威脅國家安全的設備及服務。"},{"pid":"a23039f4529745c3d318b273ef033f1e3a848acb","tid":2444960,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20201506_PO_%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20201506_PO_%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD.png&h=e665866f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da63f9b271ef0bac63daf7e8259376a91900d6e9","tid":2444960,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a23039f4529745c3d318b273ef033f1e3a848acb","tid":2444960,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T08:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20201506_PO_%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20201506_PO_%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD.png&h=e665866f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"回力鏢"},{"pid":"ad79ee209e7b335efb6ac818f05ab2710dac99d0","tid":2444960,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}